171  public LineItemProjection name(String locale, List<String> acceptLanguage) {
172    getFields().put("name", null);
173    getInputArguments().computeIfAbsent("name", k -> new ArrayList<>());
174    InputArgument localeArg = new InputArgument("locale", locale);
175    getInputArguments().get("name").add(localeArg);
176    InputArgument acceptLanguageArg = new InputArgument("acceptLanguage", acceptLanguage);
177    getInputArguments().get("name").add(acceptLanguageArg);
178    return this;
179  }
